text: Gocho Milev (born 20 October 1944) is a Bulgarian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Bulgaria Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:People from Dobrich Province
